3. cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) - The paper involves the construction of codes with specific properties, which is a topic related to discrete mathematics. 
4. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) - The paper discusses upper and lower bounds for the maximum size of DNA codes, which is a topic related to computational complexity. 
5. cs.CG (Computational Geometry) - Although not directly related, the topic of DNA codes and their construction can be seen as a problem in computational geometry, as it involves finding optimal solutions in a high-dimensional space.
